              "Value": "HenroCup® is designed and intended for beverage and food only. HenroCup® has been developed by Danish occupational therapists to ensure a high-quality cup for people that experience loss of strength and coordination. HenroCup® is not BPA Free and should not be used by children under the age of 3 years old. HenroCup® is designed with 2 wide handles to give a firm grip, the shape of the cup and handles ensures that you can drink without bending the neck. The bottom of the cup is wide to help it stand firm on the table and reduces spillage. "
